    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="引子"><a href="#引子" class="headerlink" title="引子"></a>引子</h1><p>闲得蛋疼没事做，拿Tkinter捏了个计时器软件，tk简直是我用过最难受的GUI</p><h2 id="预览"><a href="#预览" class="headerlink" title="预览"></a>预览</h2><p><img src="/2022/08/30/Reload-Timer/windows-light.png"></p><p>Run in Windows 11, Light Mode</p><p><img src="/2022/08/30/Reload-Timer/windows-dark.png"></p><p>Run in Windows 11 , Dark Mode</p><p><img src="/2022/08/30/Reload-Timer/fedora_light.png"></p><p>Run in Fedora 36, Light Mode</p><p><img src="/2022/08/30/Reload-Timer/settings.png"></p><h2 id="define"><a href="#define" class="headerlink" title="define"></a>define</h2><p>没有复杂操作，界面简单，解压缩即可开箱使用</p><p>随意切换浅色、深色主题 （双击计时数值区）</p><p>可以置于顶层以便管理时间</p><p>提供对定时关机的支持，并可随时撤销（请不要把关机倒计时作死设为0）</p><p>提供软件设置</p><h2 id="帮助"><a href="#帮助" class="headerlink" title="帮助"></a>帮助</h2><p>更多了解请看程序目录下的帮助文件</p><h2 id="下载"><a href="#下载" class="headerlink" title="下载"></a>下载</h2><p>Windows On 蓝奏云：<a href="https://akara.lanzoux.com/iTIcp0j6p6fc">https://akara.lanzoux.com/iTIcp0j6p6fc</a></p><p>Linux On 蓝奏云：<a href="https://akara.lanzoux.com/icXAI0j6pw1e">https://akara.lanzoux.com/icXAI0j6pw1e</a></p><h2 id="开源"><a href="#开源" class="headerlink" title="开源"></a>开源</h2><p>On Github: <a href="https://github.com/CavDev/Reload-Timer">https://github.com/CavDev/Reload-Timer</a></p><p>更多描述见仓库</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
