    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="MD-速查文档"><a href="#MD-速查文档" class="headerlink" title="MD 速查文档"></a>MD 速查文档</h1><p>[TOC]</p><h2 id="基本语法"><a href="#基本语法" class="headerlink" title="基本语法"></a>基本语法</h2><h3 id="标题（Heading）"><a href="#标题（Heading）" class="headerlink" title="标题（Heading）"></a>标题（Heading）</h3><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown"><span class="hljs-section"># H1</span><br><span class="hljs-section">## H2</span><br><span class="hljs-section">### H3</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="加粗（Bold）"><a href="#加粗（Bold）" class="headerlink" title="加粗（Bold）"></a>加粗（Bold）</h3><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown"><span class="hljs-strong">**bold text**</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="斜体（Italic）"><a href="#斜体（Italic）" class="headerlink" title="斜体（Italic）"></a>斜体（Italic）</h3><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown"><span class="hljs-emphasis">*italicized text*</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="引用块（Blockquote）"><a href="#引用块（Blockquote）" class="headerlink" title="引用块（Blockquote）"></a>引用块（Blockquote）</h3><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown"><span class="hljs-quote">&gt; This is a blockquote</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="有序列表-（Ordered-List）"><a href="#有序列表-（Ordered-List）" class="headerlink" title="有序列表 （Ordered List）"></a>有序列表 （Ordered List）</h3><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span cla