    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Tkinter-快速上手"><a href="#Tkinter-快速上手" class="headerlink" title="Tkinter 快速上手"></a>Tkinter 快速上手</h1><p><em><strong>本文由</strong>NsX7</em><em>编写，第一次写文档，如有遗漏，欢迎指出  &#x3D;D</em>**</p><p>2021.10.4 14:08:20</p><h2 id="1-1-Tkinter的简介"><a href="#1-1-Tkinter的简介" class="headerlink" title="1.1 Tkinter的简介"></a>1.1 Tkinter的简介</h2><p> Tkinter 是 Python 内置的标准 GUI 库，可以运行在绝大多数的操作系统上（如Windows, Mac, Linux, Unix）</p><p>下面是一个简单的示例，当你将它编译后，你将会得到一个标题为tk的窗体</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> tkinter <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> *   <span class="hljs-comment">#引用tkinter</span><br><br>mainwindow = Tk() <span class="hljs-comment"># 初始化</span><br><br>mainwindow.mainloop()   <span class="hljs-comment">#使窗体进入信息循环</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>我们还可以向其中加入一些窗体的属性</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> tkinter <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> *<br><br>mainwindow = Tk()<br>mainwindow.geometry(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;350x400&quot;</span>)     <span class="hljs-comment">#规定窗体大小</span><br>mainwindow.title(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Hello World&quot;</span>)    <span class="hljs-comment">#规定窗体标题</span><br><br>mainwindow.mainloop()<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="1-2-控件"><a href="#1-2-控件" class="headerlink" title="1.2 控件"></a>1.2 控件</h2><p>Tkinter提供了许多的控件，我们可以选择控件来把它放在窗体上</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> tkinter <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> *<br><br>mainwindow = Tk()<br>mainwindow.geometry(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;300x300&quot;</span>)<br>mainwindow.title(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Hello World&quot;</span>)<br><br>lb1 = Label(text=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Hello World! 你好世界！&quot;</span>, fore=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;green&#x27;</span>)<br>btn1 = Button(text=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;ClickMe&quot;</span>, fore=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;red&#x27;</span>, cursor=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;hand2&quot;</span>)<br><br>lb1.pack()<br>btn1.pack()<br><br>mainwindow.mainloop()<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>我们可以在写完控件后将其赋值，再布局</strong></p><p>也可以不赋值，如同下面这么写</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python">Label(text=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Hello World! 你好世界！&quot;</span>, fore=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;green&#x27;</span>).pack()<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>“pack”是一种布局方式，在不传入参数的情况下，会以默认形式从上到下排版</strong></p><p><strong>在Tkinter中，控件必须写出布局方式，不然控件将不会出现在窗体</strong></p><hr><p>以下是pack的一些参数</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python">side:按扭停靠在窗口的哪个位置<br><br>　　　　left: 左<br><br>　　　　top: 上<br><br>　　　　right: 右<br><br>　　　　botton: 下<br><br>　　fill:填充<br><br>　　　　x:水平方向填充<br><br>　　　　y:竖直方向填充<br><br>　　　　both:水平和竖直方向填充<br><br>　　　　none:不填充<br><br>　　expand:<br><br>　　　　yes:扩展整个空白区<br><br>　　　　no:不扩展<br><br>　　anchor:<br><br>　　　　N:北  下<br><br>　　　　E:东  右<br><br>　　　　S:南 下<br><br>　　　　W:西 左<br><br>　　　　CENTER:中间<br><br>　　padx:x方向的外边距<br><br>　　pady:y方向的外边距<br><br>　　ipadx:x方向的内边距<br><br>　　ipady：y方向的内边距<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>除了pack以外，还有grid和place两种布局方法，现在无需太过意了解pack，我们在后面会讲到后两种布局方式。</p><hr><p>下面来讲控件属性</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python">text=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Hello World! 你好世界！&quot;</span>, fore=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;green&#x27;</span> <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在控件后的括号内，我们可以编写控件的属性，声明一个控件属性的语法如下</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python">xxx=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span>, yyy=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>前段写属性名称，后段写属性的值，中间用&#x3D;号来赋值。在写下一个属性的时候，中间要用逗号隔开，然后再写下一个属性</p><hr><p><strong>Tkinter中内置了许许多多的控件及控件属性，由于时间（偷懒）问题不在此编写</strong></p><p><strong>但我找到了一篇讲的很好的介绍Tkinter控件及属性的文章，大家可以去👀👇</strong></p><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_43533825/article/details/88658691">https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_43533825&#x2F;article&#x2F;details&#x2F;88658691</a></p><h2 id="1-3-事件处理"><a href="#1-3-事件处理" class="headerlink" title="1.3 事件处理"></a>1.3 事件处理</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> tkinter <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> *<br><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> tkinter <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> messagebox<br><br>mainwindow = Tk()<br>mainwindow.geometry(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;300x300&quot;</span>)<br>mainwindow.title(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Hello World&quot;</span>)<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">btn1_Click</span>():<br>    hello = messagebox.showinfo(title=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Hello World&quot;</span>, message=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;你好世界&quot;</span>)<br><br>lb1 = Label(text=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Hello World! 你好世界！&quot;</span>, fore=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;green&#x27;</span>)<br>btn1 = Button(text=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;ClickMe&quot;</span>, fore=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;red&#x27;</span>, command=btn1_Click, cursor=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;hand2&quot;</span>)<br><br>lb1.place(x=<span class="hljs-number">5</span>, y=<span class="hljs-number">5</span>)<br>btn1.place(x=<span class="hljs-number">5</span>, y=<span class="hljs-number">28</span>)<br><br>mainwindow.mainloop()<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>将此段编译一下，点击按钮，你会得到一个内容为“你好世界”的信息框，那这是怎么实现的呢？</p><p>这就是我们在这里要讲的：“事件处理”</p><hr><p>在Tkinter中，绑定事件是一件很容易的事</p><p><strong>我们在控件的属性中使用 command 来绑定一个事件</strong></p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python">Button(text=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Hello&quot;</span>, command=xxx)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>后面则加上事件名称，事件则就是一个 def 函数，如果你用心观察，也许你也发现了示例代码中的 btn_click 事件。</strong></p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-comment"># 例子</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> tkinter <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> *<br><br>mainwindow = Tk();<br>mainwindow.title(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;事件&#x27;</span>)<br>mainwindow.geometry(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;300x300&#x27;</span>)<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">btn1_click</span>():<br>    Label(text=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;嘿，你点了我！&#x27;</span>).place(x=<span class="hljs-number">50</span>, y=<span class="hljs-number">50</span>)<br><br>btn1 = Button(text=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;点击我&#x27;</span>, command=btn1_click, height=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>, width=<span class="hljs-number">12</span>)<br><br>btn1.place(x=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>, y=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>)<br><br>mainwindow.mainloop()<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里可能有人要问了，那么上面那个信息框是怎么实现的？</p><p>这些则是使用messagebox实现的</p><p><strong>messagebox是tkinter中可以用来显示信息、确认信息的一个模块</strong></p><p><strong>messagebox有着许多参数，在此不加赘述，可见下方链接 ↓</strong></p><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/Bugest/article/details/81557112">https://blog.csdn.net/Bugest/article/details/81557112</a></p><p>下面是示例</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> tkinter <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> *<br><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> tkinter <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> messagebox <span class="hljs-comment"># 使用messagebox需先引用</span><br><br>mainwindow = Tk();<br>mainwindow.title(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;事件&#x27;</span>)<br>mainwindow.geometry(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;300x300&#x27;</span>) <span class="hljs-comment"># 窗体大小</span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">btn1_click</span>():  <br>    messagebox.showwarning(title=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;WARNING&#x27;</span>, message=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;警告，电脑将在30秒后爆炸&#x27;</span>)<br>    <span class="hljs-comment"># 输出一个警告窗体，其中 title= 后写窗体标题， message= 后写信息</span><br><br>btn1 = Button(text=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;点击我&#x27;</span>, command=btn1_click) <span class="hljs-comment"># 放置按钮，绑定事件</span><br><br>btn1.place(x=<span class="hljs-number">3</span>, y=<span class="hljs-number">3</span>) <span class="hljs-comment"># 布局</span><br><br>mainwindow.mainloop()<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="1-4-总结"><a href="#1-4-总结" class="headerlink" title="1.4 总结"></a>1.4 总结</h2><p>此文为快速入门，虽是快速入门，其实Tkinter本来就是这么简单，虽然它可能比不上目前流行的一些GUI框架或是Python的GUI框架，但不可不说Tkinter也是个不错的选择。</p><p>在你看完了这篇文章后，相信你对Tkinter已经有了一定的认识，能做出自己的程序了，如果你还希望进一步学习Tkinter，这里有几份推荐给你</p><hr><p>#Tkinter详细教程#  <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/RNG_uzi_/article/details/89792518?ops_request_misc=%7B%22request_id%22:%22163577762916780255274290%22,%22scm%22:%2220140713.130102334..%22%7D&request_id=163577762916780255274290&biz_id=0&utm_medium=distribute.pc_search_result.none-task-blog-2~all~top_positive~default-1-89792518.first_rank_v2_pc_rank_v29&utm_term=tkinter">Python-Tkinter图形化界面设计（详细教程 ）_Zhangfei Wang-CSDN博客_tkinter</a> </p><blockquote><p><strong>u1s1，这个比我讲得详细多了</strong></p></blockquote><p>#Tkinter的place布局#  <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/Riven_h/article/details/117531522?ops_request_misc=%7B%22request_id%22:%22163577762916780255249776%22,%22scm%22:%2220140713.130102334.pc_blog.%22%7D&request_id=163577762916780255249776&biz_id=0&utm_medium=distribute.pc_search_result.none-task-blog-2~all~first_rank_ecpm_v1~rank_v31_ecpm-8-117531522.first_rank_v2_pc_rank_v29&utm_term=tkinter">tkinter的Frame布局_Riven_h的博客-CSDN博客</a></p><blockquote><p><strong>Tkinter的Place布局方法</strong></p></blockquote><p>#Tkinter的grid布局#  <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_43708622/article/details/107134216?ops_request_misc=%7B%22request_id%22:%22163577762916780255249776%22,%22scm%22:%2220140713.130102334.pc_blog.%22%7D&request_id=163577762916780255249776&biz_id=0&utm_medium=distribute.pc_search_result.none-task-blog-2~all~first_rank_ecpm_v1~rank_v31_ecpm-17-107134216.first_rank_v2_pc_rank_v29&utm_term=tkinter">tkinter-grid布局详解_渔道的博客-CSDN博客</a></p><blockquote><p><strong>Tkinter的Grid布局方法</strong></p></blockquote><p>#Tkinter窗体设置#  <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/m0_51713294/article/details/110529034?ops_request_misc=&request_id=&biz_id=102&utm_term=python">怎么用python tkinter做窗口边框美化？_m0_51713294的博客-CSDN博客</a></p><blockquote><p><strong>关于Tkinter窗体的一些设置，挺实用的</strong></p></blockquote><p>#Tkinter学生管理系统#  <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq1123642601/article/details/90760485?ops_request_misc=%7B%22request_id%22:%22163577913716780261963745%22,%22scm%22:%2220140713.130102334..%22%7D&request_id=163577913716780261963745&biz_id=0&utm_medium=distribute.pc_search_result.none-task-blog-2~all~sobaiduend~default-1-90760485.first_rank_v2_pc_rank_v29&utm_term=python+tkinter%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F&spm=1018.2226.3001.4187">python+tkinter学生管理系统_WF帆少的博客-CSDN博客_tkinter学生管理系统</a></p><blockquote><p><strong>Tkinter一个做学生管理系统的小例子</strong></p></blockquote><p>#Tkinter五子棋#  <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_40298768/article/details/106082306?ops_request_misc=%7B%22request_id%22:%22163577913816780261938236%22,%22scm%22:%2220140713.130102334.pc_all.%22%7D&request_id=163577913816780261938236&biz_id=0&utm_medium=distribute.pc_search_result.none-task-blog-2~all~fi